We, Merchant Banking of Taishin Securities, are one of the leading investment banking division in Taiwan, specialized in domestic and cross-border M&A, buy-out, privatization and fund-raising transactions. We are dedicated in providing customized and sophisticated solutions for our diversified customer bases ranged from Jumbo companies, PE funds, VC, family offices and high net worth individuals.

Due to continuingly growing businesses, we are looking for talents interested in investment banking area to join and grow with us.

【Investment Banking Analyst】-  Job descriptions

(1) Perform industry research – collect, analyze and present on industry information including market trend, supply chain, business opportunities, etc;
(2) Generate M&A ideas and strategies;
(3) Produce pitch book – make an affluent and clear pitch book for internal and external counterparties under strict time constraint;
(4) Perform financial model – make a sufficient financial forecast and verify the rationality of assumptions;
(5) Relationship management and deal sourcing – maintain relationship with exist clients and develop new clients to identify potential business opportunities;
(6) Others – other ad-hoc assignments.

