job_detail:
In this role and with this legal team, we would like to grow together on your career path, you will not be expected to be a corporate legal expert with necessary skillset, but also be in charge of a comprehensive project to provide solutions for creating valuable business.

You will have a mentor to help you get started smoothly. We are committed to be your partner during this rewarding journey. Ready to pave your way to a bright and value-added career? Apply to this position and get to know more about your future opportunities in KIOXIA Taiwan Corporation (formerly Toshiba Memory Taiwan Corporation).

Key Areas of Responsibilities:
1.	Advise on general corporate law matters, including counsel regarding compliance with trade regulations and all other applicable corporate governance requirements;
2.	Assist in preparing Board and shareholder meeting documents and ensuring compliance with internal subsidiary management policies;
3.	Work closely with relevant departments to conduct internal audit projects; and
4.	Support research and ad-hoc requests.

Qualifications:
